{"tid":1878748,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［支爆近了］華為與孟晚舟 被美加控竊美國公司商業秘密等罪","createTime":"2020-02-13T19:33:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-14T14:02:06.000Z","uid":239336,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"548390916ebd65fa83e770c582e7f3b1f2fbc678","tid":1878748,"uid":239336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-13T19:33:14.000Z","msg":"檢察官向紐約布魯克林聯邦法院提交替代起訴書（superseding indictment）。該法院去年1月對華為及孟晚舟提出13項起訴，包括串謀及欺詐銀行等，當時西雅圖法院也對華為提出另外10項指控。<br />\n新控罪指華為從事竊取美國公司商業秘密的活動長達「數十年」，為了發展全球業務，陰謀盜用六間美國公司的知識產權。控罪提及的商業秘密包括互聯網路由器原始碼、手機天線技術及機械人技術等。<br />\n華為亦被指觸犯《反勒索及受賄組織法」（Racketeer Influenced and Corrupt Organizations Act，簡稱RICO Act）。新指控亦針對華為與受制裁國家如伊朗和北韓的關係等。<br />\n加拿大2018年12月1日應美國政府司法互助要求，在溫哥華機場拘捕華為太子女孟晚舟，去年1月高調宣佈針對華為和孟晚舟的23項控罪，並正式提出引渡孟晚舟到美國受審。加拿大法院現正審理孟晚舟引渡案。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20200214&amp;s=10793140&amp;a=60596513\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20200214%26s%3D10793140%26a%3D60596513&d=3BA04jbrysekxL3Ytp5IvR68f20TVEdZexmFDfnZHo4%3D&h=bbdcfa6d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20200214%26s%3D10793140%26a%3D60596513&h=829d16dd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20200214&amp;s=10793140&amp;a=60596513</a><br />\n<br />\n侵侵好波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68c25b502ef0b70124511dc60a4152a47408a1f5","tid":1878748,"uid":239336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-13T19:35:40.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2630dd4b61aee405d4f7ab84bec9832c3dbbcfa8","tid":1878748,"uid":239336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T12:22:26.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a88ec22e463a510e6f7071618fabc4cced777a39","tid":1878748,"uid":15084